name hyphen-turkish
category TLCore
revision 78069
catalogue tkhyph
shortdesc Turkish hyphenation patterns.
longdesc Hyphenation patterns for Turkish in T1/EC and UTF-8 encodings.
longdesc Auto-generated from a script included in the distribution. The
longdesc patterns for Turkish were first produced for the Ottoman Texts
longdesc Project in 1987 and were suitable for both Modern Turkish and
longdesc Ottoman Turkish in Latin script, however the required character
longdesc set didn't fit into EC encoding, so support for Ottoman Turkish
longdesc had to be dropped to keep compatibility with 8-bit engines.
depend hyph-utf8
depend hyphen-base
execute AddHyphen 	name=turkish 	lefthyphenmin=2 	righthyphenmin=2 	file=loadhyph-tr.tex 	file_patterns=hyph-tr.pat.txt 	file_exceptions=
containersize 3868
containerchecksum c28157280dad4ac8ce003a8a68c546dda74dc51fd137280b883e3249306f1dca58611986a275ec43af71e1038c0b10f473577321cd8bbe325a29aff2c7237fcc
srccontainersize 2724
srccontainerchecksum b3da2b2ed5760e9945b7653e7a344951d2a5b8ed5c6c74fc28e1061a534a92231cfefb31bd311bf1d7d42668c0b1a6c09727a5f7ff91089790ee1e176910d00d
runfiles size=5
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/loadhyph/loadhyph-tr.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/ptex/hyph-tr.ec.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/tex/hyph-tr.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/txt/hyph-tr.pat.txt
catalogue-ctan /language/hyphenation/tkhyph.tex
catalogue-license other-free
catalogue-topics hyphenation turkish
